175 A.3d 156 MATTHEW KEEFE, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. XAVIER FERNANDEZ, ET AL., DEFENDANTS, AND BOROUGH OF RIDGEFIELD, RIDGEFIELD FIRE DEPARTMENT, TRUSTEES OF RIDGEFIELD LADDER COMPANY NO. 1, GARY CHARTOFF, AND ANDREW CHARTOFF, DEFENDANTS-RESPONDENTS, AND MELISSA CHARTOFF, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-241 September Term 2017

079899 October 26, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003760-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
